ess to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=a8863043\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"abcd5fb29fcf756fdac9dcf72901c0fbd7f50455","tid":1396560,"uid":107221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29cd167634ced163e6ebdb0ca272fc0296e64210","tid":1396560,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"個PASSWORD幾耐世紀前用過?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:40:47.000Z","msg":"通常都係娛樂用嘅email pw呢 公事分開"},{"pid":"a1e18b379e3ba02c4f556c8423d25b8dc0d53604","tid":1396560,"uid":13879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abcd5fb29fcf756fdac9dcf72901c0fbd7f50455","tid":1396560,"uid":107221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29cd167634ced163e6ebdb0ca272fc0296e64210","tid":1396560,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"個PASSWORD幾耐世紀前用過?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:40:47.000Z","msg":"通常都係娛樂用嘅email pw呢 公事分開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"䡛pw<br />\nEnable 2FA<br />\n唔同account 用唔同pw<br />\n只能減低機會，冇可能完全防止"}]}